   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Volume 47 of The Collected Works is comprised of two books by Watchman Nee on the subject of the church and authority in the church.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>The Orthodoxy of the Church is based on a Bible study conducted by Watchman Nee during the period between 1942 and 1948.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>This section of Volume 47 has been previously published as a separate title.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Authority and Submission, based on a series of messages given by Watchman Nee in his training at Kuling Mountain in 1948 through 1949, contains two distinct but related parts.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>In 1988 the Living Stream Ministry published the first part under the title Authority and Submission, covering the general subject of spiritual authority and submission.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Volume 47 of The Collected Works includes a second, previously untranslated, part covering the matter of being God's deputy authority.</S>
   </TEXT>
